title: Cherry Compote Cake
content:
If you fancy a cake that out of the ordinary, then look no further. Try our Cherry Compote Cake. Freshly baked in the kitchen just for you. It's not too sweet and not too sour but just right as you savour the tangyness and yet sweetness of the cherries. The crust would balance the flavours of the compote. \
